<p>There are 4 Capability Statements defined to describe the expectations for this implementation guide:</p>

<li><a href="CapabilityStatement-notification-sender.html">Notification Sender CapabilityStatement</a></li>
<li><a href="CapabilityStatement-query-responder.html">Query Responder CapabilityStatement</a></li>
