<h3 id="the-following-table-summarizes-how-these-capabilitystatements-applies-to-the-da-vinci-notification-actors">The following table summarizes how these CapabilityStatements applies to the Da Vinci Notification Actors</h3>

<table class="grid">
  <thead>
    <tr>
